org.linqs.psl.model.rule

Interface GroundRule

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    UnweightedGroundRule, WeightedGroundRule
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractGroundArithmeticRule, AbstractGroundLogicalRule, GroundLinearConstraint, GroundLogLoss, GroundValueConstraint, LDAgroundLogLoss, LossAugmentingGroundRule, UnweightedGroundArithmeticRule, UnweightedGroundLogicalRule, WeightedGroundArithmeticRule, WeightedGroundLogicalRule

    public interface GroundRule
    A function that either constrains or measures the compatibility of the values of GroundAtoms.

    GroundRules are templated by a parent Rule.
